Alias My_D0   			D0
Alias My_anti-D0 		anti-D0

ChargeConj My_anti-D0 		My_D0

Decay My_D0
  1.0 K- pi+ pi+ pi-		LbAmpGen DtoKpipipi;
Enddecay
CDecay My_anti-D0

Decay B+sig
  1.0 My_D0 pi+ My_anti-D0  	FLATSQDALITZ;
Enddecay
CDecay B-sig

End
